  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This partnership aims to provide real-time analysis, evidence-based solutions, and actionable recommendations to help policymakers and other stakeholders mitigate the impact of COVID-19 in LMICs and prepare for future global pandemics.


The partnership will focus on three cross-cutting and overarching objectives:
a) Advancing a more resilient global health system and fit-for-purpose preparedness and response infrastructure for LMICs: 

b) Strengthening global health supply chains and promoting sustainable models for global health innovation and access to make markets work better for the poor in LMICs 
c) Advancing an effective and coordinated international response to economic challenges in LMICs</narrative>
  </description>
